# 2D Rotate

   transform: rotate(20deg); The rotate value provides the ability to rotate an element from 0 to 360 							  degrees

# 2D Scale

   transform: scale(.75);    allows you to change the appeared size of an element.
   transform: scaleX(.5);    scaleX value will scale the width of an element.
   transform: scaleY(1.15);  value will scale the height of an element.

# 2D Translate

   transform: translate(-10px, 25%);   change the position of an element.
   transform: translateX(-10px);       change the position of an element on the horizontal axis 
   transform: translateY(25%);         change the position of an element on the vertical axis.

# 2D Skew

  transform: skew(5deg, -20deg);	   to distort elements on the horizontal axis, vertical axis, or both
  transform: skewX(5deg);			   distorts an element on the horizontal axis 
  transform: skewY(-20deg);            distorts an element on the vertical axis. 


# Transitions And Animation

  .stage:hover .ball {
    animation-name: slide;
    animation-duration: 2s;
    animation-timing-function: ease-in-out;
    animation-delay: .5s;
    animation-iteration-count: infinite;
    animation-direction: alternate;
    animation-fill-mode: forwards;
  }

  .stage:active .ball {
    animation-play-state: paused;
  }

  @keyframes slide {
    0% {
      left: 0;
      top: 0;
    }
    50% {
      left: 244px;
      top: 100px;
    }
    100% {
      left: 488px;
      top: 0;
    }
  }

